            <head>Related Material at the Tamiment Library/Robert F. Wagner Labor Archives</head>
            <p>Jonathan Solovy, "Jewish American Volunteers and the Spanish Civil War : a study of tripartite identity" (Masters Thesis, University of Michigan, 1981) (copy at Tamiment Library; DP269.47.A46 S65 1981a)</p>
            <p>Fredericka Martin Papers (ALBA 1)</p>
