        <scopecontent id="ref1">
            <head>Scope and Content</head>
            <p>The collection consists of 53 audio cassettes which are interviews with Jewish American volunteers from the Spanish Civil War. The interviews were conducted as research for Solovy's thesis "Jewish American Volunteers and the Spanish Civil War: a Study of Tripartite Identity". They were conducted between 1980 and 1981.</p>
        </scopecontent>
