        <bioghist id="ref58">
            <head>Historical/Biographical Note</head>
            <p>Jonathan Solovy created these tapes in the course of research for his thesis "Jewish American Volunteers and the Spanish Civil War". Through contacts with vets such as Saul Wellman and Pete Smith, other veterans were contacted and interviewed. The interviews were conducted between 1980 and 1981.</p>
        </bioghist>
